--is going to let you try the bodystrider--</i>

46
00:05:48.182 --> 00:05:49.933
<i>You're dead! You can't come back!</i>

47
00:05:50.100 --> 00:05:53.437
MAN <i>2:
It's back. The Popeil Pocket Fisherman.</i>

48
00:05:53.604 --> 00:05:55.522
WOMAN <i>4:
Take my husband, take my kids...</i>

49
00:05:55.689 --> 00:05:58.692
-Are you all right?
-Hmm?

50
00:05:58.859 --> 00:06:01.361
