58
00:06:28.347 --> 00:06:30.974
<i>If Madge doesn't care,
I certainly don't.</i>

59
00:06:31.141 --> 00:06:32.309
<i>Neither do I.</i>

60
00:06:33.101 --> 00:06:35.145
Now, this here is worth a look.

61
00:06:36.980 --> 00:06:38.857
JERRY:
I'm <i>in</i> heaven

62
00:06:40.067 --> 00:06:45.822
