That I can hardly speak</i>

63
00:06:46.490 --> 00:06:48.408
<i>And I seem to find</i>

64
00:06:48.617 --> 00:06:52.329
<i>The happiness I seek</i>

65
00:06:52.829 --> 00:06:59.002
<i>When we're out together
Dancing cheek to cheek</i>

66
00:07:00.003 --> 00:07:01.838
<i>Heaven</i>

67
00:07:02.422 --> 00:07:04.883
<i>I'm in heaven</i>

68
00:07:05.801 --> 00:07:08.428
<i>And the cares that hung around me</i>

69
00:07:08.637 --> 00:07:11.431
<i>Through the week</i>

70
00:07:12.140 --> 00:07:13.392
<i>Seem to vanish</i>

71
00:07:13.600 --> 00:07:16.687
<i>Like a gambler's lucky streak</i>

72
