step off the fence! Clear that gate!

114
00:10:30.672 --> 00:10:33.258
[WHISTLE BLOWING]

115
00:10:36.219 --> 00:10:37.846
[PHONE RINGS]

116
00:10:38.013 --> 00:10:39.556
