170
00:14:55.145 --> 00:14:56.813
Why don't you just go
and make sure.

171
00:14:58.898 --> 00:15:00.859
-Uh-uh.
-I don't care where you go...

172
00:15:01.025 --> 00:15:03.319
...as long as it's not here
at this very moment.

173
00:15:07.615 --> 00:15:08.908
All right.

174
00:15:17.792 --> 00:15:18.835
